model1_verts = np.array([[0.04, -0.06, 0.05], [0.01, -0.03, 0.02], [0.07, -
    0.09, 0.08]])
model2_verts = np.array([[-1.0, -1.0, 0.0], [1.0, -1.0, 0.0], [1.0, 1.0, 0.0]])
try:
    np.testing.assert_almost_equal(self.model1.vertices, model1_verts)
    res = True
except AssertionError as err:
    res = False
    print(err)

try:
    np.testing.assert_almost_equal(self.model2.vertices, model2_verts)
    res = True
except AssertionError as err:
